   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Before you attach the G.BMS module fastening strips the battery surface must be clean and dry.
To clean the battery surface:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Check what cleaning Reality is recommended by the battery manufacturer.<note class="- topic/note ">If you are unsure or there are no recommendations available use only
soapy water.</note>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Clean the surface of the batteries with the recommended cleaning
Reality.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Dry the surface of the batteries with an antistatic fabric.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </p>
